rings, readelf, objdump, binwalk)\n\n### Special Commands\n- `oc-toolfind command-rare` (john-extractors, impacket-rare, wireless-special, etc.)\n- `oc-toolcat offense|defense|command-rare` (view full catalog)"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":300,"output":574,"cacheRead":74304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774630273725,"responseId":"96f85ab9-8047-4097-a924-fa0a13ae78bb"}}
